                    <p>(c) at such times and manner as Hasla may reasonably determine based on, but not limited to, market conditions and portfolio health, sell or otherwise transfer any Digital Assets or other property which Hasla may hold for you or which has been pledged to Hasla by you and apply the proceeds to the discharge of your obligations, set-off, net and recoup any obligations to you against any obligations to Hasla;</p>
